text: Lykovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Bolshesosnovskoye Rural Settlement, Bolshesosnovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 87 as of 2010. The village has one street. == Geography == It is located 13 km south-east from Bolshaya Sosnova. ==References== Category:Rural localities in Bolshesosnovsky District
title: Lykovo
